الأربعاء، الجمعة 9 صباحًا إلى 1 ظهرًا ومن 2 مساءً إلى 6 مساءً بتوقيت المحيط الهادي القياسي\n<h3>لطلب موعد بالمختبر، يرجى التسجيل أدناه:</h3>\n[توضع وحدة الاتصال هنا] (مطلوب توجيه من أجل هذا النموذج)\";s:2:\"id\";i:341;s:6:\"filter\";s:2:\"db\";}'),(3339,1248,'bbl_job_meta','_edit_lock'),(3340,1248,'bbl_meta__edit_lock','1443746521:1'),(3341,1248,'bbl_job_meta','_edit_last'),(3342,1248,'bbl_meta__edit_last','1'),(3343,1248,'bbl_job_meta','_thumbnail_id'),(3344,1248,'bbl_meta__thumbnail_id','246'),(3345,1248,'bbl_job_meta','page_subtitle'),(3346,1248,'bbl_meta_page_subtitle',''),(3347,1248,'bbl_job_meta','_g_feedback_shortcode'),(3348,1248,'bbl_meta__g_feedback_shortcode','[contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'First Name\' type=\'name\' placeholder=\'First Name\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Middle Name\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'Middle Name\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Last Name\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'Last Name\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Email Address\' type=\'email\' placeholder=\'Email Address\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'App Name\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'App Name\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Number of Users\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'Number of Users\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Countries Where App is Available\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'Countries Where App is Available?\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Languages Supported\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'Languages Supported\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Are you testing a mobile app or a mobile website?\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'Are you testing a mobile app or a mobile website?\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'What OS are you targeting?\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'What OS are you targeting?\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'App Description\' type=\'textarea\' placeholder=\'App Description\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Comments\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'Comments\'/][contact