ungsi Di Mana Pun</h3>\nLab Inovasi Internet.org membantu pengembang memahami cara kerja aplikasi mereka di berbagai belahan dunia. Lingkungan uji lab meniru berbagai kondisi jaringan, mirip simulator penerbangan untuk programmer komputer. Memahami kinerja aplikasi di berbagai negara membantu pengembang menciptakan pengalaman berkualitas tinggi bagi semua orang, bahkan warga di area dengan lebar pita rendah.\n\n&nbsp;<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-146\" src=\"http://vip.local/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/TBD-Image.jpg\" alt=\"TBD-Image\" width=\"960\" height=\"680\" />\n<h3>Lokasi:</h3>\nFacebook Headquarters\n1 Hacker Way\nMenlo Park, CA 94025\n<h3>Jam kerja:</h3>\nSenin, Rabu, Jumat \n9.00 - 13.00, dan 14.00 - 18.00 PST\n<h3>Untuk minta waktu di lab, harap daftar di bawah ini:</h3>\n[modul kontak di sini] (butuh arahan untuk formulir ini)\";s:2:\"id\";i:672;s:6:\"filter\";s:2:\"db\";}'),(3419,1252,'bbl_job_meta','_edit_lock'),(3420,1252,'bbl_meta__edit_lock','1443746521:1'),(3421,1252,'bbl_job_meta','_edit_last'),(3422,1252,'bbl_meta__edit_last','1'),(3423,1252,'bbl_job_meta','_thumbnail_id'),(3424,1252,'bbl_meta__thumbnail_id','246'),(3425,1252,'bbl_job_meta','page_subtitle'),(3426,1252,'bbl_meta_page_subtitle',''),(3427,1252,'bbl_job_meta','_g_feedback_shortcode'),(3428,1252,'bbl_meta__g_feedback_shortcode','[contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'First Name\' type=\'name\' placeholder=\'First Name\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Middle Name\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'Middle Name\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Last Name\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'Last Name\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Email Address\' type=\'email\' placeholder=\'Email Address\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'App Name\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'App Name\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Number of Users\' type=\'text\' placeholder=\'Number of Users\'/][contact-field required=\'1\' label=\'Countries Where App is Available\' type=\'text\'