y lives. But something is missing, something huge—over half of the world is still unconnected. Until everyone has access, we will all be incomplete. Our goal is to provide everyone in the world with access to the internet, for free. Imagine the difference an accurate weather report makes for a farmer planting crops. Think about the power of putting an encyclopedia into the hands of a child who doesn\'t even have a textbook. Now, imagine what they might be able to contribute when the world can hear their voices. We’re not doing this to make the internet better. We\'re doing this to connect us all. Because the more we connect, the better it gets.</p>','Our Mission','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2015-10-30 16:43:15','2015-10-30 16:43:15','',5,'http://internetorg.jam3.net/en/blog/2015/10/30/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1700,1,'2015-10-30 17:21:20','2015-10-30 17:21:20',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1700','','','2015-10-30 17:21:20','2015-10-30 17:21:20','',0,'http://internetorg.jam3.net/en/',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1701,1,'2015-10-30 17:21:20','2015-10-30 17:21:20',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1701','','','2015-10-30 17:21:20','2015-10-30 17:21:20','',0,'http://internetorg.jam3.net/en/',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1702,1,'2015-10-30 17:21:20','2015-10-30 17:21:20',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1702','','','2015-10-30 17:21:20','2015-10-30 17:21:20','',0,'http://internetorg.jam3.net/en/',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1703,1,'2015-10-30 17:22:51','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','','','','2015-10-30 17:22:51','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://internetorg.jam3.net/bn/?post_type=bbl_job&p=1703/',0,'bbl_job','',0),(1704,1,'2015-10-30 17:40:04','2015-10-30 17:40:04','','Internet.org is','','new','closed','closed','','internet-org-is-2','','','2015-10-30 17:40:04','2015-10-30 17:40:04','',0,'http://internetorg.jam3.net/en/blog/bbl_job/internet-org-is-2/',0,'bbl_job','',0)